---
title: Smart Chicken and Spinach Croquettes with Sweet Potatoes, Green Beans and Garlic Parm Dipper
description: This dinner is all about the Parm! It adds a deliciously cheesy flavour in the meatballs, plus acts as a crunchy garlicky topper on the beans as well as a delightful dipper for roasted sweet potatoes! Smart and indulgent all in one!
